  "technical": {
    "architecture_summary": "GPU marketplace on Solana. Jobs submitted via API, CLI, SDK, or web dashboard. Nosana Grid matches GPU supply (hosts) with compute demand via Solana smart contracts. Supports Docker containers, HuggingFace model loading, S3 resources, health checks, and confidential execution. Sub-second finality enables micro-payments.",
    "consensus_mechanism": "Solana PoS (underlying chain). Nosana uses Anchor smart contracts for job matching and payments.",
    "what_is_onchain": "Job matching, payments, staking (xNOS), governance voting, token transfers. All on Solana.",
    "what_is_offchain": "GPU compute execution, model inference, Docker container orchestration, data processing.",
